## Template SQL base

```sql
WITH origem AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM minha_origem
),

tratada AS (
    SELECT
        campo_1,
        campo_2,
        CAST(dt_ref AS date) AS dt_ref,
        COALESCE(valor, 0) AS valor
    FROM origem
),

agregada AS (
    SELECT
        campo_1,
        SUM(valor) AS vl_total,
        COUNT(*) AS qtd_registros
    FROM tratada
    GROUP BY 1
)

SELECT *
FROM agregada;
```

